MiniBlog is a dynamic, Instagram-like web application that displays posts in a beautiful and responsive layout. The app allows users to view posts by filtering them into three categories: Latest,All and Popular. Each post contains an image a heading a description and an associated date. The app fetches data from a server-side API, displaying content dynamically. Bootstrap is used for the layout to ensure a responsive design adapting smoothly to different screen size.
Technologies used(HTML, CSS, Javascript, Bootstrap)
API: Fetch API
